   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>MH 875, recto: (1) A (2-3) reckoned solidus (4) has come to me (5) from you, (6) Peter (son of) Athanasius, (7) for the daphane of the (8) fifth year, total one solidus.  (9) Mechir 30, indiction 5.  Senouthius, (10) the headman, I sign.  (11) Athanasius, son of Papnoute, (12) signs.  (13) Mena (son of) Paam (14) signs.</ab>
